{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/移动端适配/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Orainsink's blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"89ad8cab-3085-59fa-982d-9232ae4c98ce","excerpt":"1.meta viewport 在head标签加 作用是使viewport的宽度等于设备的宽度，不允许用户手动缩放，让viewport的宽度等于设备的宽度。 2.媒体查询 media query. 加在link标签内： css中直接用 3.动态rem  在sass文件中添加","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%AB%AF%E9%80%82%E9%85%8D/#1meta-viewport\">1.meta viewport</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%AB%AF%E9%80%82%E9%85%8D/#2%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2-media-query\">2.媒体查询 media query.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%AB%AF%E9%80%82%E9%85%8D/#3%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81rem\">3.动态rem</a></li>\n</ul>","html":"<h4 id=\"1meta-viewport\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1meta-viewport\" aria-label=\"1meta viewport permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.meta viewport</h4>\n<p>在head标签加</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>viewport<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">content</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>作用是使viewport的宽度等于设备的宽度，不允许用户手动缩放，让viewport的宽度等于设备的宽度。</p>\n<!--more-->\n<h4 id=\"2媒体查询-media-query\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2-media-query\" aria-label=\"2媒体查询 media query permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.媒体查询 media query.</h4>\n<p>加在link标签内：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>style.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">media</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>(max-width:320px)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>/*link会下载好，但只在宽度小于320px时生效*/</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>css中直接用</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\">&lt;style>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@media</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">min-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>376px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> and <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">max-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>425px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>green<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n&lt;/style>/宽度376px~425px之间时生效/</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"3动态rem\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81rem\" aria-label=\"3动态rem permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3.动态rem</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n     <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> pageWidth <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerWidth\n     document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">write</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'&lt;style>html{font-size:'</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span>pageWidth<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token string\">'px;}&lt;/style>'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//1rem等于1/10屏幕宽度</span>\n </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p> 在sass文件中添加</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\">@function px2rem( $px ){\n  @return px/designWidth*10 + rem;\n}\n$designWidth : 640; // 640 是设计稿的宽度 \n.child{\n    width:px2rem(320);\n}</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"移动端适配","date":"2018/07/05","description":null,"tags":["前端","css"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/移动端适配/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/关于本博客/"},"frontmatter":{"title":""}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/使用Karma-Mocha进行单元测试/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"使用Karma+Mocha进行单元测试"}}}}}